{"tid":1686634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜仲有「分化撚」同「五毛」嘅日子","createTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:34:30.000Z","uid":131766,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42ea36dbb3cb7612fc48dceaa5adbeeec64bb8be","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得呢排愈黎愈多「分化撚」同「五毛」不斷放負搞分化？<br />\n明明我地就黎贏，擺明係佢地怕怕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想帶風向令我地灰鳩內鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 你會咁諗係因為你未醒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好想知你地覺得贏左啲乜<br />\n撤回咗條將啲存在問題引爆嘅導火線？<br />\n<br />\n口號嗌得幾大聲唔去做始終都係口號<br />\n一指出問題就成為你地口中嘅分化撚同五毛<br />\n屈鳩人割你而唔係去諗點樣改善 到底邊個割邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線其實係condom 相信大家心入面都好清楚 見到啲冷氣軍師理所當然咁話咩義士唔止係矛仲係盾 嘩屌你好意思講出口 更癲嘅係大部分人都係咁諗 明知已經瀕臨絕種仲唔諗下點保護佢地 自己懦弱當人condom仲要大大聲講出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kMcqxT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kMcqxT.png&h=970526e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3M4gEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3M4gEz.png&h=b1e37e3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdmLLxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdmLLxW.png&h=3bd35d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1OeDSX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1OeDSX.png&h=3db62f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明愈黎愈多人心灰意冷畀你地搞到唔再出黎你地仲不斷打飛機 講事實又唔岩你地聽<br />\n大部分人心入面最想有人係鏡頭面前被殺 死得愈慘畫面愈靚 外國就會幫拖我就坐享其成fat fat la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/US7yUWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUS7yUWS.png&h=48b264e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從來唔想付出 當人權法係救世主合理化自己嘅懦弱 人地肯做埋你嗰份仲要割鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n割頸個男仔連罩都唔戴想班狗放低戒心 拎晒前途出黎諗住係鏡頭前開個頭畀你地跟 嘩屌即刻畀你地話係狗係大陸派黎 最後冇人記得佢 哈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2b0zoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2b0zoT.jpg&h=9e86cf71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇黎真係要入到集中營先可以ff點升級<br />\n<br />\n除咗有狗扮阻膠仲有啲真心嘅撚樣覺得還拖個畫面唔夠慘 唔慘啲邊有人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為畀藍屍斬嘅撞嘅未到你地同你地屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綁起班大愛阻膠開紅海推晒上前線做人盾 畫面仲靚呀我同你講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzZhBFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzZhBFm.png&h=7d8b7b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iL4p063.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiL4p063.png&h=fa08d489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRP5Ly1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRP5Ly1.png&h=202342df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續將所有責任推畀人 要人做你枝矛做埋你個盾 好快可以一齊除低口罩入集中營做肉便器<br />\n話跟生日拎材料出去有幾多人真係有攞 跟本係要由後排不斷整不斷傳上去 <br />\n真係好驚嘅其實要企遠幾條街係高位做哨<br />\n<br />\n好多人屌晒鬼其實係因為自從612同71之後都冇做到啲咩可以提升士氣嘅嘢 每日起身睇到嘅都係尋晚又捉咗幾多人 畀狗咬到幾傷 幾多死因冇可疑<br />\n成個ig facebook都係得啲好嬲好嬲 口號不如轉做香港人好嬲喇<br />\n<br />\n你感受唔到有幾失望係因為你匿埋係電話電視後面<br />\n或者你出去攞完物資打個卡就返屋企 好多人仲會做你地口中嘅分化撚係因為仲未放棄 哀莫大於心死 當有一日死咗心唔再理 就唔會再有動力出返黎 每次都用不流血不被捕做藉口包裝自己嘅懦弱迫人和你鳩 <br />\n但次撚次咪又係流血被捕 屌你覺得單方面無止境嘅消耗可以去到幾時？<br />\n<br />\n612同71正正因為大家都好絕望當end game先做到啲嘢吊住條命 希望有覺悟嘅可以狠心啲出埋星期六唔好再出黎 城牆一日唔倒下 住係城堡嘅小公主永遠都唔會醒<br />\n<br />\n平安夜定個無底線嘅死線普天同慶啦 如果到時仲未大搜捕完又未變返港豬又多咗人醒先算喇 或者一覺瞓醒有其他星球/靈體幫拖呢<br />\n中間呢段時間陪下重要嘅人 段練下 做下港豬好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78aeed7f1b2504124ebd18d5b8227e177f3ab5cc","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"8fe532c5ac3b75b5ab20dfe9b254176dff333cda","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78aeed7f1b2504124ebd18d5b8227e177f3ab5cc","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"晴晴你灰鳩未"},{"pid":"35b2b318081a2818cc0937818b2247d03443224f","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe532c5ac3b75b5ab20dfe9b254176dff333cda","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78aeed7f1b2504124ebd18d5b8227e177f3ab5cc","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"晴晴你灰鳩未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"屌話唔灰都呃你啦"},{"pid":"080676959c88720f4d7517647c6fa98ac6f81653","tid":1686634,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"冇5毛風向撚就代表會熄登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e85dc48fdafe90902362e89766a676ac609fecd","tid":1686634,"uid":234089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"183981ab3ad1b4e6d03c5e4964c2d56d5b722d93","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b2b318081a2818cc0937818b2247d03443224f","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe532c5ac3b75b5ab20dfe9b254176dff333cda","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78aeed7f1b2504124ebd18d5b8227e177f3ab5cc","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"晴晴你灰鳩未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"屌話唔灰都呃你啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"見到哎豬班黃豬fd子 等啲狗收隊先彈出黎隔成條街拍片屌狗 真係好大衝擊 對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccfc6d9325d57a858d4879f97e353f7d2421e10","tid":1686634,"uid":238424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"係連燈講真話得到既留言通常都係<br />\nhello sir<br />\n又block一件分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦，訓左幾耐？仲......？用下個腦"},{"pid":"a1f4242ac10bb3b590dc15df1a8a77193675443c","tid":1686634,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"04e4585b2bcc4b74f7a2b94c6dab1f328fdfc795","tid":1686634,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"樓主意思：清醒 = 放棄？"},{"pid":"15c65aa2bc4c820d26d2ad89f3f9d638ef259253","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ccfc6d9325d57a858d4879f97e353f7d2421e10","tid":1686634,"uid":238424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"係連燈講真話得到既留言通常都係<br />\nhello sir<br />\n又block一件分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦，訓左幾耐？仲......？用下個腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:39:50.000Z","msg":"呢班先係五毛<br />\n當然入面仲有一堆以為自己醒咗嘅黃屍豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6e42ed4543213002629a2e11d1f01ede038b9d","tid":1686634,"uid":185320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"坐言起行<br />\n將革命融入生活當中好重要"},{"pid":"7a0040cd4485c8a57026561e9ac3d98b3c41c084","tid":1686634,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"不是看到希望而堅持<br />\n而是堅持才看到希望"},{"pid":"feb58258ddaa20e9baef84b2ab63ae2b37d73667","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183981ab3ad1b4e6d03c5e4964c2d56d5b722d93","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score