0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"呢個post 已經推爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【突發】11.2愛丁堡、遮打、尖沙咀不反對已批！11.2  100萬級流水式和平集會 真正部署！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685372</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>112 「求援國際 堅守自治」公民活動日真正run down如下：<br />\n<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 到維園支持 逾100位候選人合法選舉聚會<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 環保方式前往 中環<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環愛丁堡廣場一帶 （美國集會已批不反）<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環遮打花園一帶 （紙鶴活動已批不反）<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"189bae5a7c7323abcb134148a2cfe2c20ca4163b","tid":1686634,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"曱甴王<br />\n甴近平<br />\n江甴文<br />\n毛甴東"},{"pid":"c50d62a5e3144ff29d981c7f0f50e26ebfae550d","tid":1686634,"uid":312698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人明個種感受，試過開花，係沙田叫人出去做野，全部都仲唱歌，企係商場入面，唔聽你講"},{"pid":"b1de477f0d867c1b7ae4a00d888231ed35356eee","tid":1686634,"uid":31317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"搵人分享下和變勇心路歷程，做左咁多個月freeride，唔係咁易轉職，唔會因為你一篇野就改變。"},{"pid":"6b951bdbaf521a7e768da2bf24bfc9a9b43fa2b9","tid":1686634,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1de477f0d867c1b7ae4a00d888231ed35356eee","tid":1686634,"uid":31317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"搵人分享下和變勇心路歷程，做左咁多個月freeride，唔係咁易轉職，唔會因為你一篇野就改變。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌完咪又係反吭<br />\n大叔懶得再屌"},{"pid":"71d99fb25ea9f2fa9f3a32f5ab2dfb0ebf416e6e","tid":1686634,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb58258ddaa20e9baef84b2ab63ae2b37d73667","tid":1686634,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183981ab3ad1b4e6d03c5e4964c2